== Confirm Email

**Authentication not required**

When a user signs up, the welcome email will have a link to `<front_url>/confirm-email/<id>/<token>`.  Front end react app will make a POST request as documented below.

[source]
----
POST /users/:id/confirm-email
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`token` | `string` | Token from the URL in the email sent.
|===


